{"word":"G2235 - ἤδη - ḗdē - ay'-day - Already","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἤδη</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ḗdē</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ay'-day</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Already</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"இப்பொழுது, ஏற்கனவே, அதற்குள்ளாக - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"now, already"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Apparently from <a href=\"#/G2228 - ἤ - ḗ - ay/2228\">G2228</a> (or possibly <a href=\"#/G2229 - ἦ - ē - ay/2229\">G2229</a>) and <a href=\"#/G1211 - δή - dḗ - day/1211\">G1211</a>; <i>even now:</i> - already, (even) now (already), by this time.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}